&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*** Please note that NEL staff At-Risk candidates will be given priority consideration ***&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join the Business Performant Team as an Escalations Analyst.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The post holder will be responsible for managing escalations on behalf of the customer, liaising with the relevant support and management teams within the organisation to expedite each issue to either a satisfactory conclusion or to a point where it can be transferred back to an appropriate resolver team&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJon RichmondJob titleBusiness Performance ManagerEmail addressjon.richmond@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
